title: SC EP:580 Confessions Of A Pastor Part 2
itunes:title: SC EP:580 Confessions Of A Pastor Part 2
description: Randy returns to the show. Tonight we discuss how Randy became a pastor. He had several life experiences that led up to where he is at in life. Randy started out in life working in a night club, what led to him becoming a pastor will surprise you.
